column3: Not sure what the objective here is, but I’m trying to understand if you’re trying to attract viewers to the channel - and the brand, or is this some self initiated personal flogging of your previously crafted and finely tuned marketing plan?? If this is your new campaign, no worries, I know where my hat is - and my wallet and can see myself out.

These are great. Cycling needs more of this. Good fun. Educational. Creative. As for all the negative comments on these I can only say one thing. If you can’t appreciate art you can at least respect it.
No no no no no no no, no no no no no no! Not this time Gal not this fuckin time, no!
You guys are trying a bit too hard on that artsy fartsy stuff
